PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1994-1476 of August 30, 1994 by deleting from the Schedule thereto the words "Martin Stone Toronto, Ontario"; and appointment of MARTIN STONE of Toronto, Ontario, as part- time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending August 30, 1997, effective November 1, 1996.
